name: db-migration.yml
configuration:
spring:
  liquibase:
#    enabled: true
    change-log: classpath:db/changelog/db.changelog-master.xml
  datasource:
    driver-class-name: org.postgresql.Driver
    url: "jdbc:postgresql://postgres-anton/ttm_camunda?ApplicationName=nttm-db-migration"
    username: "postgres"
    password: "1"
  jpa:
    database: postgresql
    hibernate:
      ddl-auto: none
    database-platform: org.hibernate.dialect.PostgreSQL95Dialect
    properties:
      hibernate:
        connection:
          release_mode: after_transaction
        temp:
          use_jdbc_metadata_defaults: false
  jackson:
    serialization:
      fail_on_empty_beans: false
    deserialization:
      read_date_timestamps_as_nanoseconds: false
  jmx:
    default-domain: db-migration-app-jmx
  application:
    name: "nttm-db-migration"
  bpm:
    business_key: "createdFromMyCode"
    camunda_url: "http://nttm-camunda-6784/engine-rest/"
    camunda_creds: ""
server:
  port: 8084
logging:
  config: classpath:log4j2-dev.yaml
  level:
    org.hibernate: error
    org.hibernate.SQL: error
    org.zalando.logbook: info
logbook:
  format:
    style: http
  exclude:
    - "**/metrics"
